# Naming Conventions

## File Naming
- Dates: `YYYY-MM-DD`
- Times: `HHMMSS` (24-hour)
- Scripts: `descriptive_name.py`
- Config: `config_name.json|.py`
- Tests: `test_*.py`
- Logs: `*.log`
- Org files: `descriptive_name.org`

## Python Documentation
### File Headers
```python
"""
Brief description of file purpose.

Created by: [Code Name]
Date: [YYYY-MM-DD]
Project: Triad Docker Base
"""
```

### Standards
- Google-style docstrings
- Comments explain WHY, not what
- Document function parameters and returns

## Org File Headers
```org
#+TITLE: [Descriptive Title]
#+AUTHOR: [Code Name]  
#+DATE: [YYYY-MM-DD]
#+FILETAGS: :relevant:tags:
```

## Requirements
- Verify necessity and location before creating files
- Check naming compliance
- Update architecture files when creating new files
- Document rationale in conversation logs
